You can simply ask Alexa to control your HUVI Robot Vacuum by connecting Alexa to HUVI in a few simple steps:
(1). Download the “HUVI” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure your HUVI Robot Vacuum in the “HUVI” app and change appropriate name for your device;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “HUVI” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “HUVI” skill, and you'll be navigated to “HUVI” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like:
Alexa, turn on Huvi
Alexa, turn off Huvi
